name: You are the baguette that I want
name_original: You are the baguette that I want
description:
Web version: https://wolologames.com/games/totespare/

Objective:

  • Cook the bread and introduce it on the big cat anus

Controls:

  • A-D repeatedly to mash the bread
  • F to launch it to the oven
  • Space to launch it to the big cat
  • Left-Right arrows for moving the big cat
